ColorPanel
==========
A decorative mood light.

This design is based on the S12G Micro EVB (https://github.com/hotwolf/S12G-Micro-EVB).

Directories:
============
|
+-Hardware              - Hardware related information
|
+-Software              - Source code (ASM and Forth)
|
+-Preview               - Processing sketches to try out display patterns
|
+-Tools                 - Development tools
|
+-Subprojects           - Repository clones of the projects that the ColorPanel
                          is based on

